OpenDomotic is a low cost Domotic Solution licensed under the GNU GPL v2 license.

General Features:
    GUI based on Qt
    Low cost hardware 
    Eigth zones with movement and magnetics sensors
    Ligths auto on/off by zone
    AlarmClock
    Two modes (nigth/travel)
    Power Consumption (historics and price/month)
    Other Sensors (ligth,temperature,gas leakage detector)
    Reconfiguration over serial
    ... and more 

